{"article_id":"WLFwINjvxqNYvkp5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"BIRMINGHAM , Ala. -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Every time","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"he ' s run for statewide office here ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Roy Moore has had Johnny Williams ' vote .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"\" I ' ve seen him fighting at them fires ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"and I just believe in him , \"","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"the 77-year-old retired bus charter company owner said in an interview .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Moore , Alabama ' s Senate Republican nominee , has been bleeding support from some conservatives in the weeks","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"since the allegations of past sexual misconduct have surfaced .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"But the candidate ' s famously loyal supporters","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"- who have long supported the Christian conservative in statewide races for chief justice , governor and senator for two decades -","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"aren ' t leaving him .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"whoever put this thing together is trying to take him out ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and we just don ' t believe it down here , \"","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"said Williams ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"who lives in Pike Road .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Moore has denied the allegations","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"that he engaged in sexual activity or sought romantic relationships with teenage females","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"when he was in his thirties .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"\" It ' s way bigger than Roy Moore .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"It is the direction of our country. \"","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"- 68-year-old Ann Eubanks of Birmingham","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Though he 's taken a hit ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Moore 's polling has recovered in recent days ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"with the Real Clear Politics polling average showing the Republican leading Democratic nominee Doug Jones 49 percent to 45 percent .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"In interviews , Moore ' s supporters say","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"they ' re sticking with him","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"because of what the election means","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"for passing President ' s Trump legislative agenda .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"\" I am a policy voter , \"","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"said 68-year-old Ann Eubanks of Birmingham ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"who leads a tea party group .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"\" And I refuse to send a far-left liberal Democrat to Congress .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"There ' s too much at stake in this country at this point with the balance of the Senate at critical mass . \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Eubanks cited future nominations to the Supreme Court , repealing ObamaCare , building the wall and immigration proposals as issues","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the president will need every vote","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"he can muster in the Senate .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"\" It ' s way bigger than Roy Moore , \"","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Eubanks said .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"\" It is the direction of our country . \"","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Still , Moore is struggling to win over the support of other Alabama voters","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"who usually vote Republican ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"something","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"which has made the race much closer","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"than expected .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Over coffee and waffles at a Waffle House here , 66-year-old Richard Barnett said","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"he wasn ' t a fan of Moore","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"before the allegations surfaced","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and won ' t vote for him","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"though he usually votes Republican .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"\" The last Democrat","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"I voted for","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"is Jimmy Carter , \"","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"said Barnett , the general manager of a metals and welding company .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Barnett said","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"he has \" no faith in Roy Moore ' s ability","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"to represent the majority of people \"","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"and would likely write-in Sen. Luther Strange ,","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"who lost to Moore in the primary ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"instead .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"the Hoover , Alabama community","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"he lives in","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"is predominantly Republican ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"but he ' s noticed no public support for Moore on neighbors ' lawns .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"\" You see no Roy Moore signs , \"","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"Barnett said .","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"\" You see some for Doug Jones .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"It ' s very , very unusual . \"","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"At another table at the diner on Friday , a mother from Alabaster ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"who gave her name as Sandra ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"was having breakfast with her husband .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"she ' s \" 100 percent behind Donald Trump , \"","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"but doesn ' t know","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"how she ' ll vote Tuesday .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"\" Deep down , I wish","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Luther Strange had been the candidate , \"","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"\" I ' ve seen him fighting at them fires ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and I just believe in him . ''","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"- 77-year-old retiree Johnny Williams on Roy Moore","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Winning over those voters could be the key to Moore 's victory .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Knowing","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"the path to victory involves motivating Trump ' s supporters in Alabama to vote in the special election Tuesday ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Moore ' s campaign was jubilant","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that the president held a rally Friday night just 25 miles away from the Alabama state line in Pensacola , Florida","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"to encourage people to vote for Moore .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"But at the diner in Birmingham , one waitress said","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"she ' s had enough of the election .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"As she cleared plates of hashbrowns and eggs ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"the Waffle House employee ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"named Nona ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"she couldn ' t bring herself to vote for any of the candidates Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"the behavior","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Moore has been accused of","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"is \" not Christian . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":199,"left":0,"right":198,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":198,"left":105,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":102,"right":104,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":101,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":197,"left":117,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":114,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":109,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":106,"right":108,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":7,"rig